10:10.407 --> 10:11.574
You have your own practice now.

10:11.608 --> 10:12.909
Maybe you should have
your own secretary.

10:15.478 --> 10:16.479
Is there a problem?

10:16.513 --> 10:17.880
Well, you know,
I'm just concerned

10:17.914 --> 10:19.181
that people will call,
get Lucy,

10:19.216 --> 10:20.317
and think you still work here.

10:20.350 --> 10:22.084
